00:04:38.670 --> 00:04:41.670
even when a person has an abundance,

00:04:41.670 --> 00:04:46.670
life does not result from the things he possesses.

00:04:46.670 --> 00:04:49.670
Well, that brings us back to James 4.

00:04:49.670 --> 00:04:51.670
Let's go back there again.

