but really also to our view of all of our activities.

00:05:38.670 --> 00:05:41.670
You see, in that verse in James 4,

00:05:41.670 --> 00:05:43.670
it says not just about our life,

00:05:43.670 --> 00:05:47.670
but about whether we will do this or do that.

00:05:47.670 --> 00:05:52.670
So it really applies to all of the different things that we do every day.

