Now, when we hear those reports,

00:06:03.670 --> 00:06:05.670
perhaps we begin to think right away

00:06:05.670 --> 00:06:09.670
that this is something that could only happen in a faraway land.

00:06:09.670 --> 00:06:13.670
You see, in countries like United States and Canada,

00:06:13.670 --> 00:06:15.670
those who are listening to this program,

00:06:15.670 --> 00:06:18.670
perhaps we have the attitude that,

00:06:18.670 --> 00:06:21.670
