00:06:42.670 --> 00:06:44.670
delivered and delivered to him,

00:06:44.670 --> 00:06:47.670
saying that he was banished from the country

00:06:47.670 --> 00:06:49.670
and must leave within two weeks.

00:06:49.670 --> 00:06:54.670
Now, this brother had been serving there peacefully for 23 years.

00:06:54.670 --> 00:06:57.670
Everything going along very smoothly.

00:06:57.670 --> 00:07:01.670
Two days later, the Kingdom Hall was padlocked.

00:07:01.670 --> 00:07:04.670
