00:07:10.670 --> 00:07:14.670
Well, suddenly and very unexpectedly,

00:07:14.670 --> 00:07:20.670
our work and all of our activities had been banned in that country.

00:07:20.670 --> 00:07:22.670
Well, now, what do we learn from this?

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:26.670
